caption: I am traveling to Paris. I am so happy to come to this church to pray. I am grateful to the Holy Spirit for leading me. I am grateful to the Lord.

A nice 17th century basilique tucked away in the second arrondissement of Paris, with an interesting history. It has a few chapels and quite a bit of beautiful art and decoration.  We stumbled into this church on our visit to the covered galleries, the entrance of one is just right across the street from the basilica. It sure is worth a visit, especially if you are in the area. It was so quiet and tranquil.
